Changes since v2:
 - Use CFLAGS-y to append the XEN_BUILD_PE define.
 - Check that XEN_BUILD_PE is set to 'y' in order to build the PE
   binary.

Changes since v1:
 - Rename variable.
 - Remove usage of the efi/disabled file.
